---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Updates"
eyebrow: "Latest from the practice"
heroTitle: "News, insights &"
heroTitleEm: "updates"
heroLead: "ATO updates, bookkeeping tips, small-business cash-flow insights, and whatever else we think's worth sharing."
description: "The latest updates, ATO news and bookkeeping insights from The Bookkeepers Solution."
permalink: /posts/
---

{% set postCount = collections.posts | length %}
{% if postCount > 0 %}
<ul class="posts-grid reveal">
{% for post in collections.posts | reverse %}
  <li>
    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card">
      <span class="post-card-date">{{ post.date | date("MMMM d, yyyy") }}</span>
      <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
      {% if post.data.excerpt %}<p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>{% endif %}
      <span class="post-card-arrow">Read more →</span>
    </a>
  </li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<p class="posts-empty">New posts coming soon — check back in a few weeks.</p>
{% endif %}
